DON'T BUTT IN, YOU USELESS BRAT!

00:13:02.086 --> 00:13:03.486
( Sachio groans )

00:13:03.486 --> 00:13:05.686
Nanbu: YOU KNOW,
IF YOU DON'T HIT THE OTHER GUY,

00:13:05.686 --> 00:13:08.020
YOU CAN'T WIN, NO MATTER
HOW MANY ROUNDS YOU FIGHT!

00:13:08.020 --> 00:13:10.386
Joe: AND IF HIS HITS CAN'T LAND,
I WON'T LOSE.

00:13:10.386 --> 00:13:11.753
WORKS TWO WAYS, YOU KNOW.

00:13:11.753 --> 00:13:14.320
THAT'S MY STRATEGY,
AND I'M STICKING TO IT.

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:16.453
Nanbu: YOUR STRATEGY
SUCKS BIG TIME.

00:13:16.453 --> 00:13:18.186
IF YOU GOT ENERGY
TO MOUTH OFF AT ME,

00:13:18.186 --> 00:13:21.520
THEN MAYBE YOU SHOULD CHANNEL IT
INTO SOMETHING MORE USEFUL,

00:13:21.520 --> 00:13:24.286
LIKE FEEDING
THAT SHARK BASTARD YOUR FIST!

00:13:24.286 --> 00:13:26.086
( sputters )

00:13:26.086 --> 00:13:28.220
HEY, WHAT ARE YOU‐‐( coughs )

00:13:28.220 --> 00:13:30.686
Sachio: SO THIS IS THE BIGGEST
GAMBLE OF YOUR LIFE, HUH?!

00:13:30.686 --> 00:13:33.953
WHAT A JOKE! WE'LL NEVER
MAKE IT INTO MEGALONIA

00:13:33.953 --> 00:13:35.586
LIKE THIS, YOU FAT PHONY!

00:13:35.586 --> 00:13:37.620
YOU'RE JUST LIKE THOSE JERKS
OUT THERE YELLING!

00:13:37.620 --> 00:13:39.486
JOE'S ON THAT MAT
RISKING HIS LIFE,

00:13:39.486 --> 00:13:41.720
AND ALL YOU'RE DOING
IS COMPLAINING!

00:13:41.720 --> 00:13:43.586
AND YOU'RE NO BETTER,
EITHER, JOE!

00:13:43.586 --> 00:13:45.853
‐ ( Joe gasps )
‐ Sachio: YOU REALLY THINK

00:13:45.853 --> 00:13:48.286
YOU CAN DO EVERYTHING
ON YOUR OWN?!

00:13:48.286 --> 00:13:50.286
THAT'S NOT HOW YOU...

00:13:52.286 --> 00:13:54.320
( stammering )

00:13:56.253 --> 00:13:58.253
AND I'M NOT CRYING!

00:14:02.360 --> 00:14:04.060
Nanbu: LISTEN...

00:14:04.060 --> 00:14:05.660
Joe: YEAH, I KNOW.

00:14:05.660 --> 00:14:08.360
I JUST HADN'T PROPERLY
WARMED MYSELF UP YET.

00:14:08.360 --> 00:14:09.793
IN THE NEXT ROUND‐‐

00:14:09.793 --> 00:14:11.260
Nanbu: JOE.

00:14:11.260 --> 00:14:12.826
Joe: HUH?

00:14:12.826 --> 00:14:14.926
WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING, POPS?

00:14:14.926 --> 00:14:19.526
Nanbu: LISTEN TO ME. FEAR IS
A NATURAL HUMAN INSTINCT, OKAY?

00:14:19.526 --> 00:14:22.460
IT'S THERE TO KEEP YOU
AWAY FROM DANGER.

00:14:22.460 --> 00:14:24.426
BUT BOXERS
HAVE TO TAKE THAT FEAR

00:14:24.426 --> 00:14:27.226
THAT'S SCREAMING AT THEM
AND MASTER IT.

00:14:27.226 --> 00:14:29.660
Joe: WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

00:14:29.660 --> 00:14:33.126
Nanbu: YOUR BRAIN IS TELLING
YOUR BODY THAT IT'S AFRAID.

00:14:33.126 --> 00:14:35.226
( Joe sighs )

00:14:38.993 --> 00:14:41.960
Nanbu: YOU CAN'T MOVE
THE WAY YOU USUALLY DO, CAN YOU?

00:14:41.960 --> 00:14:44.226
FEELS LIKE YOU'RE
ALL TIED UP, RIGHT?

00:14:46.426 --> 00:14:48.860
( chuckles )
SOME TOP‐TIER TRAINER I AM.

00:14:48.860 --> 00:14:52.326
I WAS SO FOCUSED ON WINNING
THE MATCH THAT I DIDN'T REALIZE

00:14:52.326 --> 00:14:54.060
YOU WERE ACTING
TOTALLY DIFFERENT THAN USUAL.

00:14:54.060 --> 00:14:55.560
WHAT DO YOU KNOW?

00:14:55.560 --> 00:14:58.860
GUESS I WAS THE ONE
THE PRESSURE WAS GETTING TO.

00:14:58.860 --> 00:14:59.700
( Sachio gasps )

00:15:01.500 --> 00:15:03.366
Nanbu: LISTEN,
SACHIO'S RIGHT ABOUT THIS.

00:15:03.366 --> 00:15:04.866
IF YOU WANNA GO TO MEGALONIA,

00:15:04.866 --> 00:15:06.800
FIGHTING ON YOUR OWN
ISN'T GONNA CUT IT.

00:15:06.800 --> 00:15:09.766
JUST REMEMBER,
THERE'S THREE OF US NOW.

00:15:12.300 --> 00:15:14.266
Joe: RIGHT. WHAT DO I DO?

00:15:15.500 --> 00:15:17.300
‐ ( Nanbu chuckles )
‐ ( horn blows )

00:15:17.300 --> 00:15:20.300
( Sachio sighs )

00:15:20.300 --> 00:15:22.366
( crowd murmuring )

00:15:27.333 --> 00:15:29.066
Samejima: HUH?

00:15:29.066 --> 00:15:30.766
( Joe laughs )

00:15:32.066 --> 00:15:33.333
( Samejima growls )

00:15:33.333 --> 00:15:34.900
Nanbu: THERE YOU GO.

00:15:34.900 --> 00:15:38.000
REMEMBER EVERYTHING
YOU PRACTICED UNDER THE BRIDGE.

00:15:38.000 --> 00:15:39.466
( Samejima roars )

00:15:39.466 --> 00:15:42.000
Nanbu: THAT RHYTHM
THAT WE DRILLED INTO YOU.

00:15:42.000 --> 00:15:43.033
( Joe laughs )

00:15:43.033 --> 00:15:44.433
Samejima: BASTARD!

00:15:47.033 --> 00:15:48.566
( Joe chuckles )

00:15:48.566 --> 00:15:51.233
Nanbu: DON'T LET HIM
LEAD OUT THERE.

00:15:51.233 --> 00:15:54.000
YOU GOTTA MAKE HIM
DANCE WITH YOU.

00:15:54.000 --> 00:15:55.700
( Samejima roars )

00:15:55.700 --> 00:15:57.033
Nanbu: THIS AIN'T
THE UNDERGROUND ANYMORE.

00:15:57.033 --> 00:16:00.140
‐ Sachio: JOE! GET HIM!
‐ Nanbu: IF YOU WANNA WIN THIS,

00:16:00.140 --> 00:16:02.940
YOU GOTTA MAKE THIS YOUR RING.

00:16:02.940 --> 00:16:04.606
( Nanbu groans )

00:16:04.606 --> 00:16:05.706
( Samejima roars )

00:16:08.873 --> 00:16:09.773
Nanbu: DO IT NOW!

00:16:22.773 --> 00:16:24.240
Referee: DOWN!

00:16:24.240 --> 00:16:26.540
Computer: ONE...

00:16:26.540 --> 00:16:28.873
‐ TWO...
‐ ( crowd gasping )

00:16:28.873 --> 00:16:29.806
Computer: THREE...

00:16:29.806 --> 00:16:31.206
Man #10: NO WAY.

00:16:31.206 --> 00:16:32.573
Computer: FOUR...

00:16:32.573 --> 00:16:35.240
‐ FIVE...
‐ Man #11: WELL, I'LL BE DAMNED.

00:16:35.240 --> 00:16:36.973
Computer: SIX...

00:16:36.973 --> 00:16:38.540
SEVEN...

00:16:38.540 --> 00:16:40.740
‐ ( crowd gasps )
‐ ( horn blows )

00:16:40.740 --> 00:16:43.473
Referee: ONE MINUTE,
17 SECONDS, IN THE THIRD ROUND,

00:16:43.473 --> 00:16:46.373
THE WINNER BY KNOCKOUT
IS "GEARLESS" JOE!

00:16:46.373 --> 00:16:48.173
( crowd murmuring )

00:16:50.973 --> 00:16:53.173
( applause )

00:17:00.946 --> 00:17:01.946
Man #12: NICE!

00:17:01.946 --> 00:17:03.346
Man #13:
YOU PROVED ME WRONG, KID!

00:17:03.346 --> 00:17:04.313
Man #14: THIS IS UNBELIEVABLE!

00:17:04.313 --> 00:17:06.446
( crowd murmuring )

00:17:09.880 --> 00:17:11.146
( Joe chuckles )

00:17:11.146 --> 00:17:12.746
Sachio: HE DID IT! HE DID IT!

00:17:12.746 --> 00:17:14.980
‐ POPS, HE REALLY DID IT!
‐ ( both laughing )

00:17:17.280 --> 00:17:18.480
Nanbu: THAT'S RIGHT,
THE BASTARD.

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:21.246
HE PULLED IT OFF. HE DID IT.

00:17:25.280 --> 00:17:27.313
( crowd cheering )

00:17:29.146 --> 00:17:30.146
( cheering fades )

00:17:30.146 --> 00:17:32.213
( engine grinding )

00:17:43.613 --> 00:17:45.480
( Sachio snoring )

00:17:47.646 --> 00:17:50.046
Nanbu: THAT'S ONE DOWN
AND FOUR MORE TO GO,

00:17:50.046 --> 00:17:52.080
JUST LIKE I PLANNED IT
FOR YOU, KID.

00:17:52.080 --> 00:17:54.213
( Joe chuckles ) OH, IS THAT SO?

00:17:54.213 --> 00:17:56.380
THEN WHO WAS THE GUY SULKING,

00:17:56.380 --> 00:17:59.113
SAYING, "SOME TOP‐TIER TRAINER
I AM," BETWEEN THE ROUNDS, HUH?

00:17:59.113 --> 00:18:00.553
SURE LOOKED LIKE YOU.

00:18:00.553 --> 00:18:02.953
Nanbu: HMM? HEY, YOU KNOW,
YOU GET AWFUL DAMN COCKY

00:18:02.953 --> 00:18:05.386
ANYTIME SOMEBODY
TRIES TO BE NICE TO YOU.

00:18:05.386 --> 00:18:07.320
Joe: OH, YEAH?
YOU WANT A PIECE OF ME, POPS?

00:18:07.320 --> 00:18:09.853
Sachio: YOU'RE NEVER
GONNA MAKE IT INTO MEGALONIA

00:18:09.853 --> 00:18:12.653
‐ LIKE THIS, YOU FAT PHONY!
‐ ( Nanbu gasping )

00:18:13.886 --> 00:18:14.920
HUH?

00:18:14.920 --> 00:18:16.420
( Sachio snores )

00:18:16.420 --> 00:18:17.986
( mutters )

00:18:19.753 --> 00:18:22.253
Nanbu: I THINK
THE BIGGEST CONTRIBUTION TODAY

00:18:22.253 --> 00:18:23.686
WAS MADE BY THAT RUNT.

00:18:23.686 --> 00:18:25.286
Joe: YEAH.

00:18:28.953 --> 00:18:30.686
♪

00:18:36.453 --> 00:18:37.820
( boxer roars )

00:18:37.820 --> 00:18:40.853
( groans )

00:18:40.853 --> 00:18:42.320
( crowd cheering )

00:18:42.320 --> 00:18:43.453
‐ Nanbu: ALL RIGHT!
‐ Sachio: AW, YEAH!

00:18:43.453 --> 00:18:44.720
( both laugh )

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:46.520
♪

00:18:47.620 --> 00:18:49.520
( no audible dialogue )

00:19:02.026 --> 00:19:03.893
( singers vocalizing )

00:19:30.826 --> 00:19:33.193
( music only continues )

00:19:46.626 --> 00:19:48.526
( music only continues )

00:20:23.666 --> 00:20:24.900
( music ends )

00:20:27.033 --> 00:20:29.700
Nanbu: HEY. ( chuckles )

00:20:29.700 --> 00:20:32.066
TEAM NOWHERE!

00:20:32.066 --> 00:20:34.133
I GUESS IT'S NOT TERRIBLE.

00:20:34.133 --> 00:20:36.500
( Joe chuckles )
NOT TERRIBLE, HUH?

00:20:36.500 --> 00:20:38.966
IT'S A HELL OF A LOT BETTER
THAN YOUR IDEA.

00:20:38.966 --> 00:20:39.900
( Nanbu grumbles )

00:20:39.900 --> 00:20:41.233
WOULD YOU JUST SHUT UP?

00:20:41.233 --> 00:20:43.333
( Sachio laughs ) COME ON, POPS.

00:20:43.333 --> 00:20:45.266
THINK ABOUT IT.
IT'S PERFECT FOR US.

00:20:45.266 --> 00:20:48.200
WE'RE SETTING OUT FROM
A DUMP LIKE THIS WITH NOTHING

00:20:48.200 --> 00:20:50.233
AND TRYING
TO GET INTO MEGALONIA.

00:20:51.900 --> 00:20:53.633
Joe: JUST GETTING STARTED.

00:20:53.633 --> 00:20:56.366
Sachio: SO, POPS,
GOT THE NEXT MATCH SET UP?

00:20:56.366 --> 00:20:58.133
THIS IS THE BIG FOURTH FIGHT,
RIGHT?

00:20:58.133 --> 00:21:00.973
Nanbu: I'VE GOT IT ALL COVERED.
I PAID A HEFTY FEE

00:21:00.973 --> 00:21:04.073
TO GET A PROFESSIONAL IN THE BIZ
TO HELP US OUT A BIT,

00:21:04.073 --> 00:21:06.573
ASKED HIM FOR THE TOUGHEST
OPPONENT HE COULD SWING.

00:21:06.573 --> 00:21:08.106
‐ ( radio chirps )
‐ OH, SPEAK OF THE DEVIL.

00:21:08.106 --> 00:21:11.206
LOOKS LIKE HE CAME THROUGH.
WE'RE ALL SET.

00:21:14.073 --> 00:21:16.473
( overlapping chatter )

00:21:22.906 --> 00:21:25.040
Man: WELL, WELL,
IF IT ISN'T NANBU.

00:21:25.040 --> 00:21:26.906
Nanbu: DON'T ACT SO SURPRISED,
MR. YABUNUMA.

00:21:26.906 --> 00:21:28.940
YOU'RE THE ONE
THAT ASKED ME TO MEET YOU HERE,

00:21:28.940 --> 00:21:30.040
FOR CRYING OUT LOUD.

00:21:30.040 --> 00:21:31.473
( Yabunuma chuckles )

00:21:31.473 --> 00:21:33.940
AS PROMISED, I FOUND A GUY.

00:21:33.940 --> 00:21:35.606
YOU COULDN'T ASK
FOR A BETTER FIGHTER

00:21:35.606 --> 00:21:36.940
THAN THIS ONE, I ASSURE YOU.

00:21:36.940 --> 00:21:38.640
Nanbu: HMM.

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:42.740
REMEMBER, I'M NOT INTERESTED
IN ANYONE RANKING 50th OR LOWER.

00:21:42.740 --> 00:21:44.473
Yabunuma: I KNOW,
AND I DELIVERED.

00:21:44.473 --> 00:21:45.540
HE'S 17th.

00:21:45.540 --> 00:21:48.173
Nanbu: 17th! DAMN, MR. YABUNUMA!

00:21:48.173 --> 00:21:50.773
I DIDN'T THINK IT'D BE ANYONE
HIGHER UP THAN 30th!

00:21:50.773 --> 00:21:52.106
YOU REALLY SURPRISED ME!

00:21:52.106 --> 00:21:54.340
LOOKS LIKE I MADE
THE RIGHT CHOICE COMING TO YOU.

00:21:54.340 --> 00:21:55.806
( Yabunuma chuckles )
YOU KNOW IT.

00:21:55.806 --> 00:21:57.706
EXCEPT, THE THING IS...

00:21:57.706 --> 00:22:00.913
THIS WAS ACTUALLY
A REQUEST FROM THE OTHER SIDE.

00:22:00.913 --> 00:22:02.980
HE WANTS TO FIGHT
THIS UP‐AND‐COMER OF YOURS,

00:22:02.980 --> 00:22:06.313
"GEARLESS" JOE, BAD,
AND I MEAN REAL BAD.

00:22:06.313 --> 00:22:07.713
( Nanbu laughs )

00:22:07.713 --> 00:22:09.680
SOUNDS LIKE
EXACTLY WHAT WE NEED.

00:22:09.680 --> 00:22:10.913
DOESN'T MATTER WHO IT IS.

00:22:10.913 --> 00:22:12.813
THE HIGHER THE RANK,
THE BETTER.

00:22:12.813 --> 00:22:15.680
SO, TELL ME,
WHO IS THIS GUY, ANYWAY?

00:22:15.680 --> 00:22:18.880
Yabunuma: HMM.
AH, SPEAK OF THE DEVIL.

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:21.680
HE SAID HE WANTED
TO GIVE YOU HIS REGARDS,

00:22:21.680 --> 00:22:23.746
SO I WAS WAITING
FOR HIM TO SHOW UP.

00:22:23.746 --> 00:22:25.213
Nanbu: HMM?

00:22:25.213 --> 00:22:27.213
( gasping )

00:22:30.213 --> 00:22:31.313
YOU.

00:22:32.780 --> 00:22:36.313
Boxer: NICE TO SEE YOU,
COACH NANBU.

00:22:41.480 --> 00:22:41.680
♪

